I"b<p><strong>Gratitude Tokens is a collaborative game designed to catalyse expressing gratitude within a community.</strong></p>

<p><img src="/assets/gratitude-token.jpg" alt="Gratitude Token" /></p>

<p>‚òÄÔ∏è This game was prototyped with <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bart-hoorweg" target="_blank">Bart Hoorweg</a> at the <a href="https://traditionaldreamfactory.com" target="_blank">Traditional Dream Factory</a>.</p>

